37:21.487 --> 37:22.987
[ Russian accent ] Colonel.

37:25.591 --> 37:27.892
[ Russian accent ] Come.

37:37.502 --> 37:39.170
Philip...

37:39.238 --> 37:41.406
I'd like you to meet Elizabeth.

37:41.474 --> 37:42.774
Elizabeth...

37:42.842 --> 37:45.744
this is Philip.

37:45.812 --> 37:47.913
Pleased to meet you.

37:47.981 --> 37:50.048
Likewise.

37:50.116 --> 37:51.984
Zhukov: I'll leave you two
to get acquainted.

37:52.052 --> 37:54.187
There is so much to talk about.

37:54.255 --> 37:56.323
Your lives up until now.

37:56.390 --> 37:58.291
Philip and Elizabeth's lives.

37:58.359 --> 38:01.694
Not the other ones...
those should never be discussed.

38:01.762 --> 38:04.531
It would be easy
to believe in the Elizabeth

38:04.599 --> 38:07.400
who grew up in Chicago,
Illinois, Philip,

38:07.468 --> 38:09.369
if you don't know
any other story.

38:09.437 --> 38:13.039
Elizabeth, you'll be less likely
to make a slip one day

38:13.107 --> 38:15.775
if there is no other version
of this man

38:15.843 --> 38:18.111
you're hiding away
in the back of your mind.

38:19.981 --> 38:21.815
Please.

38:21.883 --> 38:23.250
Sit.

38:33.162 --> 38:36.330
[ Door closes ]

38:36.398 --> 38:38.499
Would you like some tea?

38:38.567 --> 38:40.301
Yes. Thank you.

38:53.715 --> 38:55.149
Please.

