[ Ringing ]

39:17.037 --> 39:18.571
Man: Arlington Methodist.

39:18.639 --> 39:19.872
County liaison.

39:19.940 --> 39:21.975
Woman: How can I help you?

39:22.043 --> 39:24.110
Sergeant Vaugn,
Fairfax Sheriff Department.

39:24.178 --> 39:25.445
I'm looking for a John Doe...

39:25.513 --> 39:27.213
would have come in
Thursday night.

39:27.281 --> 39:30.784
Male Caucasian, 5'10",
knife wound to the stomach.

39:30.852 --> 39:32.552
Let me look.

39:32.620 --> 39:36.388
Oh, I'm sorry, Sergeant.
He expired that night.

39:36.456 --> 39:38.190
Okay, thank you.

39:38.257 --> 39:39.424
[ Sighs ]

39:39.492 --> 39:41.026
[ Receiver clicks ]

39:48.327 --> 39:51.362
Hey, neighbor!

39:51.430 --> 39:53.464
Hey, Stan.
How's the move-in coming?

39:53.532 --> 39:54.532
Oh, you know,

39:54.600 --> 39:56.134
it's long way to go.

39:56.202 --> 39:57.836
- You want a beer?
- No, thank you.

39:57.904 --> 40:00.606
But I could actually use some
jumper cables if you have them.

40:00.674 --> 40:03.242
My wife's car didn't quite make
the trip from St. Louis.

40:03.310 --> 40:04.943
Sure, come on in.

40:05.011 --> 40:06.011
Oh, great.

40:06.079 --> 40:08.280
You sure no beer?

40:08.348 --> 40:10.749
Oh, I'd love to, but I got
to go in to work.

40:10.817 --> 40:13.252
You don't even get
a day off to move in?

40:13.320 --> 40:14.920
You know, we got
this real shit storm brewing.

40:14.988 --> 40:16.589
Looks like I'm gonna be
working seven-day weeks

40:16.657 --> 40:18.224
for the foreseeable future.

40:24.798 --> 40:26.331
You having car trouble?

40:26.399 --> 40:29.701
Oh, nothing major...
cracked PCV hose.

40:29.769 --> 40:31.569
This is an Oldsmobile Delta,
huh?

40:31.637 --> 40:32.570
Yeah.

40:32.638 --> 40:33.605
'77?

40:33.672 --> 40:35.173
Mm-hmm.

40:35.241 --> 40:38.143
I wanted the Coupe.
She wanted the Sedan.

40:38.211 --> 40:40.679
So we settled on this
with a V8.

40:40.747 --> 40:44.049
Beautiful styling
with these stacked headlights.

40:44.117 --> 40:46.251
GM can't make these
fast enough, huh?

40:46.319 --> 40:49.121
Yeah, it's a great car.

40:50.824 --> 40:52.458
You weren't, uh, tempted

40:52.525 --> 40:54.793
