43:19.075 --> 43:21.344
It was a little deeper
than that.

43:24.815 --> 43:28.285
Like... like what?

43:28.352 --> 43:32.656
Hey, dad, can we get a racing
stripe on the Oldsmobile?

43:32.724 --> 43:35.292
Uh, I don't think your mom
would like that.

43:35.360 --> 43:37.996
Why not?

43:38.063 --> 43:41.532
She doesn't like new things.

